# Requirements

- Semantic HTML(element choice and organization. e.g. h1 sequencing)
- Variety of elements
  - different heading levels
  - Ordered and unordered lists
  - A form with at least 3 different input types
- Images
- Organized folder structure
- Form should post to httpbin
- Pages:
  - Home
  - 3 whatever pages
  - Contact
- Navigation should be clear and easy
- Content:
  - Have a clear site purpose that is easily understood
    from the home page

Recipe website can be a good idea to use both lists
